data.name: jsonschema
data.description: An(other) implementation of JSON Schema for Python

evidence: README install command: "$ pip install jsonschema"
"jsonschema is an implementation of the JSON Schema specification for Python." (a general-purpose validation library, not research-specific)
Usage example shows `from jsonschema import validate` and calling `validate(...)`, indicating it is imported as a library dependency rather than a standalone end-user application.
